Also, it shows that there were 60 data bytes received (data sent + padded zeroes).

I also tried using the logic analyzer but the transitions were too fast for it to capture any information. Also, I tried looking
at the data waveform with the osciloscope. I am able to see smoothened digital data due to the limited 50Mhz bandwidth of the 
oscilloscope.

